            <note xml:id="foot.f2">For CD’s observations on the part of the leaf grasped by worms when drawing different leaves into their burrows, see <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2241.xml"><hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi></ref>, pp. 64–77.</note>
